caption.text:
Another summer on the clock 🔥

🔄 A little retrospective of these last 4 ones...

✨ 2021 was such an easy going time with lots of love is in air vibes. 
✨ 2022 felt so much different and challenging. With a lot of pressure and anxiety happening. 
✨ 2023 was the toughest of all. Felt completely lost and unsecured during that time. 
✨ 2024 was like a refreshing start with still lots of soul healing to work on. 
✨ 2025  was quite a blast having the chance to swim in the ocean between 2 and 4 km almost every day. It felt like doing roller skate on a big and wild open river most of the days.
Currently enjoying the last bit of it before it gets all shivery and chaotic... 🌊

" If I told you I'd go with you
From a home I can go back to
If I told you I can see myself in you
If I told you that the way you move
I'm floating just watching you
If I told you I can see myself through you

Take me down #yourriver 
I wanna drown in you
My body starts to shiver
As I step into you
Take me down your river 
My body starts to shiver "
@monolinkmusic

caption.text:
🌿✨ كف مريم.. عشبة التوازن الهرموني للنساء ✨🌿

🔹 شو هي كف مريم؟
نبات طبي قديم (Vitex agnus-castus) اشتهر بدعمه لصحة المرأة وتنظيم الهرمونات بشكل طبيعي.

🔹 أهم الفوائد:
	•	بتنظّم الدورة الشهرية وتخفف اضطراباتها.
	•	بتقلل أعراض ما قبل الدورة (PMS) زي العصبية وانتفاخ الثدي.
	•	ممكن تدعم الخصوبة عند بعض النساء.
	•	بتخفف من أعراض سن اليأس مثل الهبات الساخنة.

🔹 موانع الاستخدام:
- ما تستخدم خلال الحمل والرضاعة.
- ما تنخلط مع أدوية الهرمونات (مثل حبوب منع الحمل أو علاجات الخصوبة) إلا باستشارة طبية.
- مش مناسبة للي عندهم أورام مرتبطة بالهرمونات.

🔹 طريقة الاستخدام التقليدية:
بتنغلى العشبة بالماء وتشرب كـ شاي عشبي ☕، أو ممكن تتوفر على شكل كبسولات/قطرات بالصيدليات.

✨ ملاحظة مهمة: النتائج بتحتاج من 2–3 شهور من الاستخدام المنتظم.

💡 تذكري: استشارة الطبيب أو أخصائي التغذية ضرورية قبل البدء بأي مكمل أو عشبة.

caption.text:
Getting Millions of Views on Social Media IS NOT luck. And I’ll show you my exact strategy in just a couple of hours!

🔥In the last 100 days I used these strategies to grow my Instagram at a rate of about 1700 followers per day for 100 Days in a row. (some days hit 6000 followers in a day 😅)

But I’ve also taught all my students how to do it too.

Like:

🔥 Maddy who got a 1 Million view video within her first 3 posts.

🔥 Mitch and Steve who got 9.3 Million views and 150,000 followers within their first week.

And we cover how to get results like this In the Part-Time Creator Academy.

We cover:
✅The algorithm secrets that make your posts go viral every single time!
✅The 4 elements of a viral video that make any video get MILLIONS of views!
✅How to generate an INFINITE number of viral video ideas!
✅How to properly post your video so it doesn’t get shadow-banned!
✅How to predictably get millions of views on EVERY ONE of your videos!
✅How to film, edit, and post your videos to maximize their chances of going viral
BONUS:
✅Confidence on Camera Mini Course - Where we teach you how to feel confident on camera and film in public

If you’re ready to take your content creation to the next level and get millions of views, tap learn more below👇
